2009-06-15  Marcus Meissner <meissner@suse.de>

	* configure.ac: use the AC_SYS_LARGEFILE macro instead
	  of the ugly largefile hacks.
	* src/libmtp.c: fix use of largefile back to the simple
	  functions instead.
