	* src/device-flags.h: added
	  DEVICE_FLAG_BROKEN_SET_SAMPLE_DIMENSIONS device flag
	* src/music-players.h: ditto. Also set Samsung YH-999 to
 	  DEVICE_FLAG_BROKEN_MTPGETOBJPROPLIST_ALL based on users
	  experience.
	* src/libmtp.c: added
          DEVICE_FLAG_BROKEN_SET_SAMPLE_DIMENSIONS device flag

