	* src/libusb-glue.c: Remove old uni-device cruft code
	* src/libusb-glue.h: Remove old uni-device cruft code
	* Replace LIBMTP_ERROR_N0_DEVICE_ATTACHED with
		LIBMTP_ERROR_NO_DEVICE_ATTACHED across entire project

